# ==============================================================================
# Binance Futures Testnet Trading Bot Environment Variables Template
# ==============================================================================
# Instructions:
# 1. Duplicate this file and rename the copy to '.env':
#    cp .env.example .env
# 2. Replace the placeholders below with your actual Testnet API credentials.
# 
# How to get your Binance Futures Testnet API credentials:
# 1. Navigate to: https://testnet.binancefuture.com
# 2. Register or log in to your account.
# 3. Locate the "API Key" panel at the bottom of the dashboard.
# 4. Click "Generate API Key" and complete verification.
# 5. Copy the generated API Key and Secret immediately (Secret is only shown once).
#
# IMPORTANT SAFETY WARNINGS:
# - Production/Live Binance API credentials WILL NOT work on the Testnet server.
# - NEVER commit your '.env' file containing active API credentials to git.
# ==============================================================================

# Your Binance Futures Testnet API Key
BINANCE_API_KEY=your_testnet_api_key_here

# Your Binance Futures Testnet API Secret
BINANCE_API_SECRET=your_testnet_api_secret_here
